channel.title: Wanna Help A Noob To Succes?
channel.description:
[center]Basicly, I am new to it all and want to get involed with it all and would like to get a superb result when the time is right, But bare in mind I do NOT want to know anything or anyone to do with LEACHING so if your going to post something dealing with LEACHING forget about the thread and leave this topic!!!
Moving on, I wanna try and get every information that I can and put it all in my big head and make something out of it in the long run after I have the information that is required to create my own Private Runescape Server.
I know it will take pretty long to learn everything and everythink, but im prepared to sit back and learn it all! After I know what is what and were things go and what I need to become a great coder, I will then be prepared to give back what is right to the community every think what everyone as taught me and after that i will also creat a journal on my adventure of becoming a great coder.
X FINGERS CROSSED X
Kind Regards Ricki [/center]
